## Channel Bot

Read-only broadcast bot that posts PumpFun activity (claims, launches, graduations, whale trades, fee distributions) to a Telegram channel. Supports GitHub/X follower enrichment, fake claim detection, and optional AI summaries via Groq.

**Platform:** Railway (recommended), Docker  
**Port:** 3000  
**Persistent Storage:** `/app/data` (claim tracker state)

### Railway Deployment

```bash
cd channel-bot
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your values

railway login
railway init
railway up
```

### Docker Deployment

```bash
cd channel-bot
docker build -t pump-channel-bot .
docker run -d \
  --name pump-channel-bot \
  --restart unless-stopped \
  -p 3000:3000 \
  --env-file .env \
  -v channel-bot-data:/app/data \
  pump-channel-bot
```

### Channel Setup

1. Create a Telegram channel
2. Create a bot via [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather)
3. Add the bot as an **administrator** of the channel (needs "Post Messages" permission)
4. Set `CHANNEL_ID` to the channel's `@username` or numeric ID (e.g., `-1001234567890`)

### Environment Variables

| Variable | Required | Default | Description |
|----------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` | ✅ | — | Bot token with channel admin permission |
| `CHANNEL_ID` | ✅ | — | Channel ID (`@channelname` or `-100xxx`) |
| `SOLANA_RPC_URL` | ✅ | — | RPC endpoint |
| `SOLANA_WS_URL` | ⬜ | Derived from RPC | WebSocket URL |
| `SOLANA_RPC_URLS` | ⬜ | — | Comma-separated fallback RPCs (rotates on 429/5xx) |
| `POLL_INTERVAL_SECONDS` | ⬜ | `30` | Polling interval |
| `FEED_CLAIMS` | ⬜ | `true` | Enable fee claim feed |
| `FEED_LAUNCHES` | ⬜ | `true` | Enable token launch feed |
| `FEED_GRADUATIONS` | ⬜ | `true` | Enable graduation feed |
| `FEED_WHALES` | ⬜ | `true` | Enable whale trade feed |
| `FEED_FEE_DISTRIBUTIONS` | ⬜ | `true` | Enable fee distribution feed |
| `WHALE_THRESHOLD_SOL` | ⬜ | `10` | Minimum SOL for whale alerts |
| `LOG_LEVEL` | ⬜ | `info` | `debug` \| `info` \| `warn` \| `error` |
| `AXIOM_REF` | ⬜ | — | Axiom.trade affiliate ref code |
| `GMGN_REF` | ⬜ | — | GMGN affiliate ref code |
| `PADRE_REF` | ⬜ | — | Padre affiliate ref code |
| `GITHUB_TOKEN` | ⬜ | — | GitHub PAT for repo enrichment |
| `GROQ_API_KEY` | ⬜ | — | Groq API key for AI summaries |
| `X_AUTH_TOKEN` | ⬜ | — | X/Twitter auth_token cookie for follower counts |
| `X_CT0_TOKEN` | ⬜ | — | X/Twitter ct0 cookie |

