## PumpOS Website

Web desktop UI with 169 Pump-Store apps.

**Platform:** Vercel, GitHub Pages

```bash
cd site
vercel --prod
# Or serve locally:
npx serve .
```

The root `vercel.json` serves the `website/` folder with SPA routing (rewrites all non-static paths to `/index.html`).

