### Health Check Endpoints

| Component | Endpoint | Method |
|-----------|----------|--------|
| Telegram Bot | `/api/v1/health` | `GET` |
| WebSocket Relay | `/health` | `GET` |
| Swarm Bot | `:3100/` (dashboard) | `GET` |
| Swarm Orchestrator | `:4000/api/bots` | `GET` |
| Dashboard | `:8080/` | `GET` |
| x402 Server | `/health` | `GET` |
| Plugin Delivery | Vercel dashboard | — |

### Recommended Monitoring

- **UptimeRobot** or **Betterstack** for endpoint monitoring (free tiers available)
- **Railway Metrics** for CPU/memory/network on Railway deployments
- **Vercel Analytics** for static site performance
- **Grafana + Prometheus** for self-hosted infrastructure
- Set up alerts for health check failures, high error rates, and resource exhaustion

