### Scaling Notes

- **Telegram bots** scale vertically — a single instance handles thousands of users
- **WebSocket relay** handles ~10K connections / 50K msg/sec on 1 vCPU — use sticky-session load balancer for more
- **Live dashboards** are static files — scale infinitely behind a CDN
- **swarm-bot** is single-instance by design (one SQLite database)
